name: Transmission89 - Brand-led digital strategy for companies ready to make waves
description:
In the year 1989 the world began a major transformation led by the release of TCP/IP into the public domain â€“ a technology holding the power to connect people around the world, unlocking a new, global economy and generation of entrepreneurs.
